            <div class="endpoint-body">
              <div class="fix-banner">
                <span class="fix-icon">🔧</span>
                <div class="fix-content">
                  <strong>Fixed from:</strong> <code>GET /createUser?name=Jo</code> — Changed to POST (creation has side effects, GET must be safe), moved data to the request body (query strings expose data in logs), removed verb from URL, added versioning.
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="endpoint-grid">
                <div>
                  <div class="detail-section">
                    <div class="detail-label">Request Body (application/json)</div>
                    <table class="params-table">
