<div class="page-header">
    <h1>🔍 REST API Design Review</h1>
    <p>A comprehensive audit of a poorly designed User Management API — every flaw identified, every fix explained, with corrected endpoints and proper HTTP semantics.</p>
    <div class="badge-row">
        <span class="badge badge-red">⚠ 4 Broken Endpoints</span>
        <span class="badge badge-green">✓ 4 Corrected Endpoints</span>
