**Every fix, summarised:**

| Original | Problem | Fixed |
|---|---|---|
| `GET /getUsers` | Verb in URL | `GET /users` |
| `GET /createUser?name=Jo` | GET mutates state; data in query string | `POST /users` with JSON body |
| `PUT /updateAllUsers` | Verb in URL; no resource ID | `PUT /users/{id}` |
| `POST /user/delete/5` | Wrong method; verb tunnelled in URL; singular noun | `DELETE /users/{id}` |
